column1: * On Track survey data is based on the number of students who responded to the 2017 On Track survey. This is a proportion of those who consented to participate in the On Track survey within the school.
** On Track survey data does not include international students.
^ This category includes destinations of respondents that are not in the labour force or education or training, or those who's destinations cannot be identified.
Not all schools are included in the table. The following exlusion rules were applied:
- Schools with less than 10 Year 12 completers or less than 10 On Track respondents were not reported.
- Schools with less than 50% consent rate, less than 50% response rate or less than 20% of the Year 12 cohort participating in the survey were not reported.
See explanatory notes for further information on data contained within this table.
